Module com.example.demo
Package com.example.demo.controller

Class LevelController

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.controller.LevelController
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameStateObserver
public class LevelController extends Object implements GameStateObserver
Manages level-specific logic, including level transitions, game updates, and overlays.

Implements the GameStateObserver interface to handle game state events such as pausing, restarting, or completing a level.
